    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The double-VANOS system has been recently serviced to ensure optimal valve timing and torque delivery across the rev range. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a limited-slip differential. To address common platform weaknesses, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight, providing the tactile hydraulic steering feedback and linear power delivery that purists demand. Finished with staggered Style 67 alloys and a quad-exit exhaust, this M3 is optimized for performance-oriented ownership.",
